1948;;Hop, Look and Listen;;American;;Robert McKimson;;Looney Tunes;;animated short;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hop,_Look_and_Listen;;Hippety Hopper escapes from a zoo, and when Sylvester first sees him, he believes that the kangaroo is actually a king-size mouse. A bulldog tries to convince the cat that there is no such thing, but when he too sees Hippety Hopper and his mother (who was searching for him), he and Sylvester hitch a ride on the water wagon.